      • parseSpliceTime

        static long parseSpliceTime(ParsableByteArray sectionData,
                            long ptsAdjustment)
        Parses pts_time from splice_time(), defined in Section 9.4.1. Returns C.TIME_UNSET, if time_specified_flag is false.
        Parameters:
        sectionData - The section data from which the pts_time is parsed.
        ptsAdjustment - The pts adjustment provided by the splice info section header.
        Returns:
        The pts_time defined by splice_time(), or C.TIME_UNSET, if time_specified_flag is false.
